{"tid":983274,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"translate (4)","createTime":"2019-01-15T22:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T23:00:23.000Z","uid":65256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d085e96f7f6ebfb7b1cd048dab21624825a2885","tid":983274,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T22:42:12.000Z","msg":"女生喜歡口甜舌滑的壞男孩，因為他們擅於用謊言來包裝自己及蒙騙你，讓你誤以為世間真有如此美好的人。他們可以騙你一時，因為他們也只愛你一時。<br />\n<br />\n相反好的男孩，你總是會覺得他們悶、無聊、無趣，又笨又粗心大意，事事盡不完美，但那不正正證明了他們沒有在你面前添加一絲不實嗎？<br />\n<br />\n若你當真如此成熟，就該為這看起來平平無奇，吃起來也乏味的糖添加些生氣，把他改變起來，使他的味道隨年月愈發芳醇，把他的外表打磨打磨也好，為他置購衣裳也好，讓他成為最切合你口味的糖就好了。<br />\n<br />\n世界上哪有這麼多天造地設的一對？愛情應該是這樣互相為對方改變的吧。"},{"pid":"3278e60f458aa9fa2a25eec411b6dcf3dd22179f","tid":983274,"uid":65256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T22:42:29.000Z","msg":"茅塞頓開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9587c4560df54d1acee20770ac6d50d8cc3e60","tid":983274,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T22:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd59d42a94705cd2d0f10ce9f8010761b673664","tid":983274,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b9587c4560df54d1acee20770ac6d50d8cc3e60","tid":983274,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T22:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T22:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a70369ee862ad67a8923b40a90e9326696435c4","tid":983274,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecd59d42a94705cd2d0f10ce9f8010761b673664","tid":983274,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score